quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  35,45,"Si tawno Alla nanngitirayno yim…ďe …ďen ko …ďe faggitorii kon, O accataano ruugayngel e dow mayri. Ko woni tun, Himo nennitana …ďe haa e lajal anndaa ngal. Si lajal ma…ď…ďe ngal hewtii, [O nanngay …ďe], tawde pellet, Alla ko Reenu…óo jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen"
  36,1,Yaa-Siin
  36,2,Mi woondirii Al*ur'aana √Īe√Īaande nden
  36,3,"Pellet, an (Nulaa…óo), ko a jeyaa…óo e Nulaa…ďe …ďen"
  36,4,E dow laawol focciingol
  36,5,"Jippinannde On Foolu…óo, Hinnotoo"
  36,6,"Fii yo a jertinir nde yim…ďe, …ďe baabiraa…ďe mun jertinanooka: …ďen ko welsindii…ďe"
  36,7,"Gom…óii konngol [lepte] jojjii e ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe; …ďen …óon gom…óintaa"
  36,8,"Menen Men wa…óii ka daa…óe ma…ď…ďe kolommbooje, …óen ko yottii…óe ka bokku…óe; hara ko …ďe Ňčallinii…ďe"
  36,9,"Men wa…ói yeeso ma…ď…ďe heedo, …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe kadi heedo, Men hippi …ďe (gite …óen); wa…óti …ďe yi'ataa [goonga]"
  36,10,"Hino fota e ma…ď…ďe, foti a jertini …ďe, maa a jertinaali …ďe; …ďe gom…óintaa"
  36,11,"Anndu ko jertintaa (ja…ďa), ko on jokku…óo Jantoore (Alqur'aana) nden, o huli Jom-Yurmeende On ka wirnii. Wewlinir mo haforaneede e mbarjaari teddundi"
  36,12,"Ko Menen woni wuurnitoo…ďe maay…ďe …ďen, Men winnda ko …ďe ardini e batteeji ma…ď…ďe. Kala huunde, Me…óen mofti nde e deftere …ďanngunde"
